"pid":"ed1eb429418e6cd520617e24588234778daee949","tid":163102,"uid":80433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:01:21.000Z","msg":"有無人知個定價去到邊....  唔想中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾十到一千既準則係點 點解差咁遠"},{"pid":"a39726f41548eb172f812b8e9a063697c87c082d","tid":163102,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:10:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就算Q版都會養到好大條架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n年中唔少人棄養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你有無養過 ？易唔易養</blockquote><br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食用魚點會難養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你個缸幾大先？"},{"pid":"e0e13a5745f071211442805ae5f76e0594342dd6","tid":163102,"uid":30487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:11:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人知個定價去到邊....  唔想中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾十到一千既準則係點 點解差咁遠</blockquote><br />\n睇大細同食水深唔深<br />\nQ版會貴過普通版"},{"pid":"f6d7c33e9b7827bfe43f7c2938dc9781a8297ad6","tid":163102,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:18:05.000Z","msg":"以下係Q版<br />\n通常都幾百蚊咁上下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/20/031723_83f486598e2da0f24188737cf955a8a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F20%2F031723_83f486598e2da0f24188737cf955a8a1.jpg&h=5d4e3872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/832FkU7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F832FkU7.jpg&h=2fa7b556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cG65Y92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcG65Y92.jpg&h=c7ae7268&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/20/031724_251b7a82ee033c5fbf5ccfc5b42fa4db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F20%2F031724_251b7a82ee033c5fbf5ccfc5b42fa4db.jpg&h=8ebca055&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a8a6b91c328de51d4c655dcaf68d26a10232010","tid":163102,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:23:04.000Z","msg":"普通版幼魚雙位數就有條<br />\n但會咁撚大條<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/20/032253_61c8c809956709e16a35f0fe90fd0f75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F20%2F032253_61c8c809956709e16a35f0fe90fd0f75.jpg&h=3d34288c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33C06J1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33C06J1.jpg&h=301b524f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Zkc8Kt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Zkc8Kt.jpg&h=cfbdb80e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7SiQ1Vc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7SiQ1Vc.jpg&h=fb3323cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89aa619c7e80e8385fa8e65a709326701f441c8e","tid":163102,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:50:30.000Z","msg":"我見你問Q版大白鯊<br />\n但貼圖就貼左普通版出黎<br />\n睇你都係唔係養開魚嗰啲人黎<br />\n我勸你都係唔好養呢啲大型食用魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一來就算Q版都見過兩尺長<br />\n如果淨係養佢一條，都要四尺缸或以上<br />\n買錯左普通版你就大獲啦<br />\n上面有圖你睇<br />\n喺佢長大成年之前你已經會頂唔順<br />\n<br />\n二來呢啲魚唔適合混養<br />\n細過口一定食落肚<br />\n可能你會喺網上睇到其他人混養到<br />\n但呢個只係一個錯覺<br />\n將來佢大條左開始食埋其他魚<br />\n十居其十啲戇鳩仔都會攞去放生<br />\n唔通啲戇鳩仔又會影相開post<br />\n話自己柒撚左搞到要放生咩<br />\n所以網上一定係見到啲人成功<br />\n就好似保險狗傳銷狗金融狗咁<br />\n<br />\n三來假設你有咁大個缸<br />\n呢啲魚粗生到不得了<br />\n養佢唔死又係一個煩惱<br />\n人會悶，到時想轉養其他魚<br />\n但條魚養左咁耐多少都有啲感情<br />\n又唔想殺佢，賣又無人要<br />\n最後都係攞去放生<br />\n早知如此何必當初呢<br />\n<br />\n無乜人養呢啲魚有好結局<br />\n淡水魚仲有好多觀賞魚<br />\n呢啲食用魚灰灰黑黑<br />\n你想睇弱肉強食嘅畫面不如養食人倉<br />\n想養大魚不如養龍魚<br />\n想養古古怪怪嘅魚不如養琵琶<br />\n有好多更好選擇<br />\n勸你都係唔好養食用魚啦"},{"pid":"1ede0c7497d070be0c48eef24887dd9b84c025dc","tid":163102,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T20:03:16.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲q版大白鯊係咩魚黎？<br />\n唔似鯊魚woo"},{"pid":"e2ef6a16df7e1512ccabd55f348d05ac36b0359b","tid":163102,"uid":80433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我見你問Q版大白鯊<br />\n但貼圖就貼左普通版出黎<br />\n睇你都係唔係養開魚嗰啲人黎<br />\n我勸你都係唔好養呢啲大型食用魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一來就算Q版都見過兩尺長<br />\n如果淨係養佢一條，都要四尺缸或以上<br />\n買錯左普通版你就大獲啦<br />\n上面有圖你睇<br />\n喺佢長大成年之前你已經會頂唔順<br />\n<br />\n二來呢啲魚唔適合混養<br />\n細過口一定食落肚<br />\n可能你會喺網上睇到其他人混養到<br />\n但呢個只係一個錯覺<br />\n將來佢大條左開始食埋其他魚<br />\n十居其十啲戇鳩仔都會攞去放生<br />\n唔通啲戇鳩仔又會影相開post<br />\n話自己柒撚左搞到要放生咩<br />\n所以網上一定係見到啲人成功<br />\n就好似保險狗傳銷狗金融狗咁<br />\n<br />\n三來假設你有咁大個缸<br />\n呢啲魚粗生到不得了<br />\n養佢唔死又係一個煩惱<br />\n人會悶，到時想轉養其他魚<br />\n但條魚養左咁耐多少都有啲感情<br />\n又唔想殺佢，賣又無人要<br />\n最後都係攞去放生<br />\n早知如此何必當初呢<br />\n<br />\n無乜人養呢啲魚有好結局<br />\n淡水魚仲有好多觀賞魚<br />\n呢啲食用魚灰灰黑黑<br />\n你想睇弱肉強食嘅畫面不如養食人倉<br />\n想養大魚不如養龍魚<br />\n想養古古怪怪嘅魚不如養琵琶<br />\n有好多更好選擇<br />\n勸你都係唔好養食用魚啦</blockquote><br />\n多謝指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38d4e32f1f93b32c5def4b0f0aec73d12f57573","tid":163102,"uid":80433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:04:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我見你問Q版大白鯊<br />\n但貼圖就貼左普通版出黎<br />\n睇你都係唔係養開魚嗰啲人黎<br />\n我勸你都係唔好養呢啲大型食用魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一來就算Q版都見過兩尺長<br />\n如果淨係養佢一條，都要四